Winning numbers drawn in ‘2 By 2’ game
LINCOLN, Neb. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Friday evening’s drawing of the “2 By 2” game were:
Red Balls: 5-20, White Balls: 3-18
(Red Balls: five, twenty; White Balls: three, eighteen)
Estimated jackpot: $22,000
¶ Top Prize $22,000.
